      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> gochujang paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>in 50ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>warm water</strong></p><p>Add 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span>[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong>, your <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your<strong> rice vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>gochujang stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1684508371816-x200.jpg",
