      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is lightly browned, reduce the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>gochujang stock</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook, stirring occasionally, for 6-8 min or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Korean-style glazed chicken</strong></p>",
