    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, combine your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>spring onion whites</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>slaw mix</strong></p>",
