    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining rice vinegar</strong>,<strong> toasted sesame oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> to the slaw mix</p><p>Mix until fully combined – this is your <strong>sesame slaw</strong></p>",
